ype":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未經授權在公園內的設施或植物上彩繪、張貼、懸掛橫幅或貼紙。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"破壞公園設施、未經授權挖掘土壤、石頭或草皮、在非指定區域傾倒廢棄物或破壞植被等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"駕車或非法停車。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"攜帶寵物或其他動物而未採取適當的保護措施並清理其排泄物。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"騎自行車、溜冰、滑板、滑冰、打高爾夫球、放風箏，以及從事其他由主管機關宣布禁止或限制的娛樂活動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亂扔垃圾、菸蒂、在指定垃圾桶外丟棄菸蒂。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"游泳、沐浴、洗滌、捕魚、釣魚、打魚叉、放生、划船、污染水質、傷害植物生命或騷擾、虐待或傷害動物。經主管機關批准的捕魚或划船活動可免於此禁令。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"晾曬衣物或其他物品。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"採摘水果、蔬菜或其他植物，未經許可。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未經許可設置任何形式的棚架。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用遊憩設施的方式不符合規定。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"隨地大小便或有其他不當行為。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出售、出租娛樂設備；或從事其他營利活動，未經許可。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"設置營火、烹飪、燃放鞭炮、或搭建遮蔽物或帳篷。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"製造過度的噪音或製造擾亂公共安寧的噪音污染。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主管機關或管理機構宣布禁止或限制的與疾病預防和傳染病控制相關的事項或公園管理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"飲酒、打架或從事其他違反公共道德的行為。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"賭博或其他有害公共道德的行為。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"攜帶危險物品。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其他由主管機關宣布禁止或限制的事項。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市龜山區公所"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"電話: (03)3203711"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-12.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-12.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"文德公園的改善重點項目"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文德公園的改善重點項目"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園禁煙, 禁酒, 並請帶走垃圾"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園是禁止吸菸及禁止飲酒。 夜間常有工地作業人員在此聚餐, 常常將吃剩的便當, 飲料罐, 酒瓶, 煙蒂留在公園。 附近居民志工幾乎需要每日清理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雖然涼亭附近就有英文告示說明公園規範, 也有大型罰款警示。 但仍需要市府仿造新北的看板: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神明在看, 加裝監視器 錄影監視中"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 才會有效！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r028-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r028-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遛狗繫狗鍊, 隨手清狗便"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園內常見自由奔跑的毛小孩， 將公園當作公廁。 無論草地或步道的遺留物都請主人帶回家！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-13.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-13.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"私人物品不要放在公園"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"個人的傢俱不要留在公園內，包含扇子, 家中擺飾品, 及私人桌子椅子等"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 來保持公園的整潔。 以往的亂象經龜山區公所整頓後, 請居民能保持這裡整潔的環境！\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園曬衣服或放置私人物品 依法裁處 5,000 元罰鍰。J"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-02.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-02.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-08.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-08.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"傢俱回收請勿堆置公園內"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"傢俱回收需要於與清潔隊約定日期的前一晚才能放置於指定地點。但不得指定公園為回收點。\n在公園內放置大型傢俱, "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"既使已通報清潔隊，仍可裁處 6,000 元 罰款。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-07.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-07.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公園內禁止騎機車/自行車"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"長樂公園旁有 Ubike 站點, 在長樂公園內常有騎車者按鈴驅趕小孩及年長者！ 原則上公園內是不能騎車的。 而騎車者喧賓奪主 按鈴驅趕行人更為惡劣。 既使在人車共用步道, 也須緩慢通過"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要按鈴"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 幼兒及年長者會被驚嚇到。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有些人認為 按鈴是提醒注意。 那麼在車道上汽車接近自行車/機車也都按喇叭提醒慢車注意， 是否合適呢？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-11.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-11.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"感謝龜山區公所的定期除草及清理工作。 公園中原有的空中電纜近期已被清除了！ 電纜下方的無障礙步道與公園間的障礙也改善完成。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在下龜山的區公所對 A7 公園的維護也更用心了, 感謝！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r037-10.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r037-10.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"公園的維護","depth":2,"text":"公園的維護","children":[{"id":"公園禁止的項目宣導","depth":3,"text":"公園禁止的項目宣導"},{"id":"文德公園的改善重點項目","depth":3,"text":"文德公園的改善重點項目"},{"id":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業","depth":3,"text":"感謝龜山區公所的維護作業"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r037.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r037.md","_extension":"md"}